# N60 Pro Compilation Configuration

This configuration is for the N60 Pro device, based on the necessary options for compiling with Passwall, Xray, and Hysteria packages.

## Target Configuration
CONFIG_TARGET_mediatek_filogic_DEVICE_netcore_n60-pro=y

## Wireless Configurations
# MediaTek MT7986 Wireless Configurations
def CONFIG_MEDIATEK_MT7986=y

# Additional required configurations for wireless components
CONFIG_B43=y
CONFIG_B43_BUILTIN=y

## Passwall Configuration
# Enable Passwall package
CONFIG_PACKAGE_passwall=y

## Xray Configuration
# Enable Xray package
CONFIG_PACKAGE_xray=y

## Hysteria Configuration
# Enable Hysteria package
CONFIG_PACKAGE_hysteria=y

# Add any additional custom options as needed.